WEBVTT

00:06:31.560 --> 00:06:32.880
And so we moved on.

00:06:34.760 --> 00:06:37.696
As I listened to story after story

00:06:37.720 --> 00:06:40.936
of these close to 700 women

00:06:40.960 --> 00:06:43.920
during that one year in prison,

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:49.256
I soon realized that crime

00:06:49.280 --> 00:06:53.440
was not what had brought
these women to prison,

00:06:54.480 --> 00:06:55.680
most of them,

00:06:56.480 --> 00:06:58.080
far from it.

00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:03.240
It had started with the education system,